snippet: Esa-Pekka Salonen led the New York Philharmonic through Beethoven and Stravinsky on Thursday, while the pianist Jeremy Denk made his Philharmonic debut.
abstract: James R Oestreich reviews performance by New York Philharmonic at Avery Fisher Hall.
lead_paragraph: Esa-Pekka Salonen led the New York Philharmonic through Beethoven and Stravinsky on Thursday, while the pianist Jeremy Denk made his Philharmonic debut.
